            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic requiescit vir venera<lb break="no" n="2"/>belis <note>sic</note> adol&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;scens <expan><abbr>nu</abbr><ex>mine</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Modoal</abbr><ex>dus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>qui vixit plus mi<expan><ex>nu</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XVI obiit <lb n="4"/>in pace quod f&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;cit m<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>ns</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">is</supplied> <lb n="5"/>F<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>br</abbr><ex>uariu</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> dies VIII cuius pater et <expan><abbr>mat</abbr><ex>er</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>in am&amp;lt;o=V&amp;gt;re ipsius <expan><abbr>titul</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> posu&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;<lb break="no" n="7"/>runt in pace 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines Christograms mit Alpha und Omega und symmetrisch flankierenden Tauben. (B): Z. 2 Numodoal statt nu(mine) Modoal(dus).</p>
            </div>
